        "setup": "Register the industry/client software through [Industries Registration for Central Server](https://esc.mp.gov.in/registration.html). After registration is completed on the MPPCB website, MPPCB provides the site-specific details needed for authentication and encryption, including `Site ID` / `site_key`, AES encryption details, and the MPPCB server RSA public key; the Open API document says the specific AES/RSA details are provided after industry registration. For remote calibration, the portal also links [Registration for Remote Calibration Check](http://erc.mp.gov.in/IMS/CRUD/CAL_registration)."
